{
  "texts": [
    "For our investigation, we selected GPT-3.5 and GPT-4 models, both of which have been fine-tuned for tool usage.",
    "For open-source options, we observed that only a limited number of small, open-source LLMs have undergone fine-tuning for tool use, and their performance was generally unsatisfactory, leading us to exclude them from further consideration.",
    "We list the detailed versions of the models and other implementation details in Appendix B.1.",
    "Output Parsing.",
    "For outputs generated by the LLMs, parsing is necessary to determine agent's next steps."
  ]
}